CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 21, 1962, pg. A5 reads: "Cited By Kay Club - Bailey Gordon (second from right), a member of the board of management of Kay Boys Club, presents citations to three area leaders during the recent dinner meeting of the club's religious education department. Left to right: Dr. John Hare, pastor of Grandview United Presbyterian Church; Dr. John Galbreath, pastor of Westminister United Presbyterian Church; Mr. Gordon and Benjamin Moore of the Social Security Administration. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Dr. John Hare, Dr. John Galbreath, holding citation for service, Bailey Gordon, and Benjamin Moore, posed in Kay Boys Club
